quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  12,1,"Alif-lam-ra tilka ayatualkitabi almubeen"
  12,2,"Inna anzalnahu qur-ananAAarabiyyan laAAallakum taAAqiloon"
  12,3,"Nahnu naqussu AAalayka ahsanaalqasasi bima awhayna ilayka hathaalqur-ana wa-in kunta min qablihi lamina alghafileen"
  12,4,"Ith qala yoosufu li-abeehi yaabati innee raaytu ahada AAashara kawkaban washshamsawalqamara raaytuhum lee sajideen"